- What are the 3 components of a User story.

1. The first part represents WHO wants to to something "As a user"

2. The second part explaines the purpose, WHY the action is needed
   "In order to send emails"

3. The third part explained WHAT is needed for it to function
   "I would like to access the compose page"


- Can you give an example of a High level user story?

As a user
In order to send emails
I would like to access the compose page

Is a user story we are working on today (week 5)
